information up

00:38:44.490 --> 00:38:47.670 align:middle line:84%
to a par of importance
with energy itself

00:38:47.670 --> 00:38:50.670 align:middle line:84%
and with physicality
so that we understand

00:38:50.670 --> 00:38:52.470 align:middle line:84%
that the universe
we live in not only

00:38:52.470 --> 00:38:55.140 align:middle line:84%
exists because of
its physicality,

00:38:55.140 --> 00:38:58.180 align:middle line:84%
but it's understood because
of this information.

00:38:58.180 --> 00:39:00.480 align:middle line:84%
And this is a
powerful new concept.

00:39:00.480 --> 00:39:04.650 align:middle line:84%
And all physical bodies have
such a holographic emission

00:39:04.650 --> 00:39:06.750 align:middle line:84%
that is available
non-locally, which

00:39:06.750 --> 00:39:11.120 align:middle line:84%
means throughout the universe,
non-locally at all times.

00:39:11.120 --> 00:39:14.640 align:middle line:84%
>> Could it be the event horizon
demonstrated by the image

00:39:14.640 --> 00:39:19.740 align:middle line:84%
on the shroud sent information
instantaneously throughout

00:39:19.740 --> 00:39:21.300 align:middle line:90%
the universe?

00:39:21.300 --> 00:39:23.820 align:middle line:84%
And does this mean
that the Resurrection

00:39:23.820 --> 00:39:26.100 align:middle line:90%
was a universal event?

00:39:26.100 --> 00:39:27.840 align:middle line:84%
>> Physics has achieved
a lot of success.

00:39:27.840 --> 00:39:30.990 align:middle line:84%
And we think that we have
