00:39:30.990 --> 00:39:33.600 align:middle line:84%
But it turns out
we know we don't.

00:39:33.600 --> 00:39:36.010 align:middle line:90%
We know there are missing links.

00:39:36.010 --> 00:39:39.030 align:middle line:84%
We know there are puzzles
and infinities cropping up

00:39:39.030 --> 00:39:40.210 align:middle line:90%
all the time.

00:39:40.210 --> 00:39:43.600 align:middle line:84%
And believe me, people are
working to find some answers.

00:39:43.600 --> 00:39:45.840 align:middle line:84%
But in spite of our
successes, there

00:39:45.840 --> 00:39:49.310 align:middle line:84%
are still some
mysteries abounding.

00:39:49.310 --> 00:39:52.100 align:middle line:10%
>> Some scientists believe the
characteristics of the image

00:39:52.100 --> 00:39:55.430 align:middle line:10%
on the shroud, such as
three-dimensional information

00:39:55.430 --> 00:39:57.590 align:middle line:10%
from a two-dimensional
photograph,

00:39:57.590 --> 00:39:59.780 align:middle line:10%
the negative aspect
of the image,

00:39:59.780 --> 00:40:03.020 align:middle line:10%
and the fact that the image that
appears on the cloth virtually

00:40:03.020 --> 00:40:06.320 align:middle line:10%
free of distortion are
basically holographic.

00:40:06.320 --> 00:40:15.740 align:middle line:90%


00:40:15.740 --> 00:40:21.800 align:middle line:84%
>> The quantum hologram is
merely a method of describing

00:40:21.800 --> 00:40:26.330 align:middle line:84%
the total emissions from an
object very much like if you

00:40:26.330 --> 00:40:27.960 align:middle line:90%
look at your fingertip.

00:40:27.960 --> 00:40:29.690 align:middle line:84%
Then you look at one
of the little swirls

00:40:29.690 --> 00:40:30.530 align:middle line:90%
