uniquely identify events

00:40:51.550 --> 00:40:52.800 align:middle line:90%
in the history of that object.

00:40:52.800 --> 00:40:55.838 align:middle line:90%


00:40:55.838 --> 00:40:58.130 align:middle line:84%
>> Could it be that events
in the history of the Shroud

00:40:58.130 --> 00:41:02.210 align:middle line:84%
of Turin are still there for
us to discover, decipher,

00:41:02.210 --> 00:41:04.475 align:middle line:90%
and understand?

00:41:04.475 --> 00:41:08.710 align:middle line:84%
If the essence of physical law
is informational, then perhaps

00:41:08.710 --> 00:41:10.900 align:middle line:84%
the image on the
shroud has given us

00:41:10.900 --> 00:41:13.450 align:middle line:84%
not only a record
of the Resurrection,

00:41:13.450 --> 00:41:16.750 align:middle line:84%
but a description
of creation as well.

00:41:16.750 --> 00:41:19.060 align:middle line:84%
Could it be that
instead of science

00:41:19.060 --> 00:41:22.600 align:middle line:84%
proving the shroud is authentic
the image on the shroud

00:41:22.600 --> 00:41:25.510 align:middle line:84%
is proving the accuracy
of the science?

00:41:25.510 --> 00:41:28.180 align:middle line:84%
In the quest for
scientific authenticity,

00:41:28.180 --> 00:41:31.930 align:middle line:84%
has the miraculous meaning of
the shroud been rediscovered?

00:41:31.930 --> 00:41:35.020 align:middle line:10%
What would it mean to the
world if scientific research

00:41:35.020 --> 00:41:37.690 align:middle line:10%
and the faith of
generations could join hands

00:41:37.690 --> 00:41:41.110 align:middle line:10%
in perfect harmony?

00:41:41.110 --> 00:41:43.000 align:middle line:84%
Up to this point,
the evidence seems

00:41:43.000 --> 00:41:46.180 align:middle line:84%
to indicate that the
1988 carbon dating

00:41:46.180 --> 00:41:48.370 align:middle line:84%
of a small piece of
the shroud fabric

00:41:48.370 --> 00:41:52.480 align:middle line:84%
was at best compromised and
at worst completely useless

00:41:52.480 --> 00:41:55.450 align:middle line:84%
in addition to which, compelling
corroborative evidence has been

00:41:55.450 --> 00:41:59.590 align:middle line:84%
examined that places the shroud
and this Sudarium of Oviedo

00:41:59.590 --> 00:42:02.590 align:middle line:90%
on the same body.

00:42:02.590 --> 00:42:05.020 align:middle line:84%
Ongoing research,
meanwhile, has uncovered

00:42:05.020 --> 00:42:07.690 align:middle line:84%
a number of other
scientific anomalies

00:42:07.690 --> 00:42:10.900 align:middle line:84%
that place the shroud squarely
over the body of Jesus

00:42:10.900 --> 00:42:13.450 align:middle line:84%
Christ at the time of
his Resurrection early

00:42:13.450 --> 00:42:17.170 align:middle line:84%
in the first century, and
at the same time squarely

00:42:17.170 --> 00:42:20.950 align:middle line:84%
at the center of a 21st
century scientific paradigm.

00:42:20.950 --> 00:42:22.870 align:middle line:84%
This suggests a
new understanding

00:42:22.870 --> 00:42:27.890 align:middle line:84%
of our place in the universe
and how it all began.

00:42:27.890 --> 00:42:29.990 align:middle line:84%
We have also seen that
scientists are now

00:42:29.990 --> 00:42:33.320 align:middle line:84%
coming to grips with a
whole new basis of physics

00:42:33.320 --> 00:42:35.210 align:middle line:84%
fundamental to the
way nature works.

00:42:35.210 --> 00:42:37.750 align:middle line:90%


00:42:37.750 --> 00:42:40.640 align:middle line:10%
In one of the most exciting
discoveries to date,

00:42:40.640 --> 00:42:44.030 align:middle line:10%
Dr. Petrus Soons points
out that there is more--

00:42:44.030 --> 00:42:46.370 align:middle line:10%
perhaps much more to
this piece of fabric

00:42:46.370 --> 00:42:50.420 align:middle line:10%
than meets the eye, even
peering through a microscope.

00:42:50.420 --> 00:42:54.560 align:middle line:84%
In 1931, Giuseppe Enri, a
professional photographer,

00:42:54.560 --> 00:42:56.870 align:middle line:84%
was commissioned to make
a photographic record

00:42:56.870 --> 00:43:00.170 align:middle line:84%
of the shroud in connection
with a royal event, which

00:43:00.170 --> 00:43:03.020 align:middle line:84%
meant many photographs
would be taken.

00:43:03.020 --> 00:43:06.560 align:middle line:84%
Dr. Soons reasoned that if
the negatives of these photos

00:43:06.560 --> 00:43:09.440 align:middle line:84%
also contained
three-dimensional information,

00:43:09.440 --> 00:43:13.290 align:middle line:84%
a full hologram of the
image might be possible.

00:43:13.290 --> 00:43:16.310 align:middle line:10%
>> I contacted Dr. Alan
Whanger and his wife, Mary,

00:43:16.310 --> 00:43:19.190 align:middle line:10%
because I knew that he was under
possession of second and third

00:43:19.190 --> 00:43:23.150 align:middle line:10%
generation copies of the
negatives of the photographs

00:43:23.150 --> 00:43:26.180 align:middle line:10%
that were made in 1931
by a doctor [INAUDIBLE]

00:43:26.180 --> 00:43:28.600 align:middle line:90%
a professional photographer.

00:43:28.600 --> 00:43:31.460 align:middle line:84%
He made available
these negatives to me.

00:43:31.460 --> 00:43:34.310 align:middle line:84%
And I brought them to
Holland and in cooperation

00:43:34.310 --> 00:43:36.170 align:middle line:84%
with the Dutch
Holographic Laboratory,

00:43:36.170 --> 00:43:37.830 align:middle line:90%
we digitalized them.

00:43:37.830 --> 00:43:40.340 align:middle line:84%
And if a professional
looks at negatives,

00:43:40.340 --> 00:43:42.310 align:middle line:84%
he can see how much
information is in it.

00:43:42.310 --> 00:43:46.823 align:middle line:84%
So we estimated that it would
be about 200 to 300 megabyte.

00:43:46.823 --> 00:43:48.740 align:middle line:10%
But it proved to be that
most of the negatives

00:43:48.740 --> 00:43:51.170 align:middle line:10%
had information up
to 1 gigabyte, which

00:43:51.170 --> 00:43:55.790 align:middle line:10%
means 4 time the informations
that we estimated.

00:43:55.790 --> 00:43:59.970 align:middle line:84%
There could be still hidden
in these digitalized files

00:43:59.970 --> 00:44:03.020 align:middle line:84%
a lot of information that
we still don't know about.

00:44:03.020 --> 00:44:05.660 align:middle line:10%
>> At first glance, we
might think that negatives

00:44:05.660 --> 00:44:09.920 align:middle line:10%
