than modern photographs.

00:44:13.580 --> 00:44:17.090 align:middle line:84%
But you have to remember that
the techniques used back then

00:44:17.090 --> 00:44:21.080 align:middle line:84%
required much longer exposure
times and more light, which

00:44:21.080 --> 00:44:25.670 align:middle line:84%
