more information on the 1931

00:44:25.670 --> 00:44:29.750 align:middle line:84%
Enri negatives than on any of
the more modern photographs.

00:44:29.750 --> 00:44:32.540 align:middle line:84%
>> Dr. Soons took the negatives
to a holographic science

00:44:32.540 --> 00:44:35.630 align:middle line:84%
laboratory in Amsterdam to
see if they would be willing

00:44:35.630 --> 00:44:37.800 align:middle line:90%
