00:44:47.420 --> 00:44:49.928 align:middle line:90%
Then they started experimenting.

00:44:49.928 --> 00:44:51.470 align:middle line:10%
And they found out
that it could make

00:44:51.470 --> 00:44:53.880 align:middle line:10%
