00:50:18.915 --> 00:50:21.720 align:middle line:90%


00:50:21.720 --> 00:50:24.270 align:middle line:84%
Every area of the
hologram sees and stores

00:50:24.270 --> 00:50:27.240 align:middle line:84%
information about
the whole image.

00:50:27.240 --> 00:50:30.090 align:middle line:84%
If you break a hologram
into multiple pieces,

00:50:30.090 --> 00:50:33.090 align:middle line:84%
you have multiple holograms,
each bearing information

00:50:33.090 --> 00:50:35.160 align:middle line:90%
about the whole image.

00:50:35.160 --> 00:50:37.610 align:middle line:84%
