00:51:09.590 --> 00:51:12.270 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps in the not
too distant future,

00:51:12.270 --> 00:51:15.440 align:middle line:84%
we may be able to create a
full unblemished hologram

00:51:15.440 --> 00:51:18.890 align:middle line:84%
from a very small area
of the shroud's image.

00:51:18.890 --> 00:51:23.480 align:middle line:84%
Indication of this can
come from a single fibril.

00:51:23.480 --> 00:51:26.330 align:middle line:84%
>> Having had a chance
to examine the holograms,

00:51:26.330 --> 00:51:30.350 align:middle line:84%
