not really that apparent

00:52:11.510 --> 00:52:13.427 align:middle line:10%
on the regular photographs.

00:52:13.427 --> 00:52:16.010 align:middle line:84%
>> The discovery of the plaque
around the neck is particularly

00:52:16.010 --> 00:52:17.460 align:middle line:90%
significant.

00:52:17.460 --> 00:52:19.790 align:middle line:84%
And being able to
identify and translate

00:52:19.790 --> 00:52:21.830 align:middle line:84%
the letters into a
meaningful phrase

00:52:21.830 --> 00:52:24.860 align:middle line:84%
suggest not only who
