00:53:48.340 --> 00:53:49.880 align:middle line:10%
had taken place--

00:53:49.880 --> 00:53:53.440 align:middle line:10%
probably the most
pivotal event in history,

00:53:53.440 --> 00:53:58.310 align:middle line:10%
which is exemplified and
witnessed by the shroud.

00:53:58.310 --> 00:54:01.370 align:middle line:10%
>> At least as far as the
Shroud of Turin is concerned,

00:54:01.370 --> 00:54:02.240 align:middle line:10%
science--

00:54:02.240 --> 00:54:04.580 align:middle line:10%
once thought to be the
enemy of all things

00:54:04.580 --> 00:54:09.170 align:middle line:10%
